# Building My Social Circles


## Relationships are mutual

- Circles of trust
- Requires investment
- Can't be unilateral
- I spend energy that matched the others
- I am intentional

## Levels of connection

- Acquaintances - weekly one-way communication
- Friends and family - occasional conversations
- Support Network - monthly sharing of hopes and fears
- Mentors - monthly sharing of hopes and fears and getting advise
- Kids - daily interactions and mutual help

